item.title: Athletic Injury Compression Wrap
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
Provides moderate support and compression to muscles without constricting breathing or muscle growth, while neoprene fabric keeps muscles warm and pliable to reduce strain and hasten recovery. Indicated for strains, cramps, pulls, and sciatica. Great for use at work or on the athletic field.

The post Athletic Injury Compression Wrap appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
This Athletic Supporter is designed to protect, lift, support and hold the testes against the body. This prevents strain on the cords and muscles during activity, helping to eliminate discomfort, and keeps them away from injury, providing unobtrusive yet consistent support for a long day of work or for vigorous sports. For correct sizing, measure the abdomen between the hips and waist. 3 inch elastic waistband retains elasticity while minimizing curling at the top and bottom. Soft knit cotton/rayon pouch gives total support. Non-roll, tubular elastic leg straps help prevent binding, wrinkling or rolling, Mesh pouch

Features:

  • 3 inch elastic waistband
  • Soft knit cotton -rayon mesh pouch
  • Non-roll, tubular elastic straps
  • Excellent supporter
  • Wash in mild suds and rinse several times in clear water to clean
  • Roll in towel to absorb moisture and dry flat
  • Do not iron
  • Do not use dryer
  • Latex free

Specifications:

  • Item Type: Athletic Jock Supporter
  • Material: Soft knit cotton -rayon mesh pouch
  • Function: Protect, lift, support and hold the testes against the body
  • Color: White
  • Washable: Wash in mild suds and rinse several times in clear water to clean
  • Iron: Do not iron
  • Weigh: 3.75 oz
  • Dimensions: 4 x 1.25 x 9 in

item.title: Shin and Achilles Protector Sleeve
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
The Achilles & Shin Gel Padding Sock is built to give you the most comfortable skiing and skating experience possible. The fabric is elastic, soft, and thin, taking less space inside the the boot and providing a highly breathable environment. Silicone padding around the tibia prevents discomfort that is commonly caused by ski and skate boots.

The post Shin and Achilles Protector Sleeve appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
• One per order
  • Toeless sock with 2mm gel polymer soft cushion pads molded to at both sides the tibia and Achilles, protecting them from abrasion, friction, and pinching when practicing sports
  • Specially indicated for ski and skate boots
  • Used under the socks with the pad either in contact to the skin or facing the sock
  • Washable and reusable
  • Two sizes

item.title: Athletic Leg Compression Sleeves
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
No Varix Sports Training Graduated Compression Leg Sleeves deliver dual, pin-point compression to the front and back of the legs to increase blood circulation and provide muscle support during athletic training, recovery, or travel.

The post Athletic Leg Compression Sleeves appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
The sleeves feature seamless gradient compression which provides wide ribbing in the front for shin support and tight ribbing in the back for calf support. Graduated ribbed compression gives you maximum support where you need it, and lighter compression where you don’t – resulting in a more comfortable fit. The compression sleeve fabric is breathable and moisture wicking, allowing the garment and athlete to stay cool, dry and light during exertion.

  • Specially designed for increased muscle support during sports training for enhanced athletic performance.
  • Use for cycling, basketball, softball, baseball, football, soccer, volleyball, running, rugby, and other high intensity sports training.
  • A great choice for sports activities, travel or everyday use. Use on long flights to reduce uncomfortable leg and ankle swelling, cramping and minor variscosities
  • Pulls moisture from your skin, dries quickly and helps regulates skin temperature. Moisture-wicking fabric helps keep you cool, dry and ready for all-day action.

Learn more about the benefits of compression.

The post Athletic Leg Compression Sleeves appeared first on AT Surgical.

item.title: Women’s Thigh High Compression Stockings
item.dc:creator: delta
item.description:
Anti-Embolism Stockings are designed to help relieve leg fatigue, uncomfortable swelling and mild to moderate varicose veins. Use on long flights to reduce uncomfortable leg and ankle swelling. These moderate support women's thigh high compression stockings are perfect for travel, business, or everyday wear. Smooth, concealing opaque fabric for an attractive appearance, with a non-binding knit-in band at calf to keep securely in place.

Made with an inspectional toe opening for post-operative patients that permits easier inspection of the toes without requiring removal of the stocking from the leg. Open toe also permits one size to fit a range of individuals. Doctor-recommended, therapeutic graduated compression helps improve circulation, relieving minor variscosities and swelling.

The post Women’s Thigh High Compression Stockings appeared first on AT Surgical.
item.content:encoded:
• 15 – 20 mmHg offers light to moderate grade compression.
  • Sold as a single pair (two stockings).
  • Made with an open toe and reinforced heel.
  • Smooth, opaque fabric is soft to the touch.
  • Available in White or Beige.

The post Women’s Thigh High Compression Stockings appeared first on AT Surgical.
